figure.p:
Note that the comparison $VAR eq '' could
          have been used instead of the function empty( $VAR
          ).

sch:let.value:
if ( $direct_target/self::tei:person )
then $direct_target
else
  if ( $direct_target[self::tei:link|self::tei:alt][@type eq 'person'] )
  then for $it in tokenize( normalize-space( $direct_target/@target ) ) return id( substring-after( $it, '#') )
  else parent::*

sch:rule.sch:report:
One or more of the items pointed to by
                    @target of this  (of type "person") does not
                    point to a 'person' element.
